<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. Cyrtandra uahukaensis W. L. Wagner &amp; Lorence (Perlman et al. 15844, isotype US)." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10497" pageId="9" pageNumber="42">Fig. 6</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
